text: Eugène Kuborn (14 November 1902 - 12 February 1991) was a Luxembourgian swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre backstroke at the 1924 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Summer Olympics and the water polo tournament at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male swimmers Category:Luxembourgian male water polo players Category:Olympic swimmers of Luxembourg Category:Olympic water polo players of Luxembourg Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Water polo players at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:People from Wiltz
